SUMMARY:Information: BANK AND MONUMENT STATIONS: From Monday 20 October 
 until November 2026. Replacement of escalators 4 and 5. These connect the 
 Northern line platforms with the District and Circle line platforms. While
  this work takes place\, the walking route between these platforms will be
  closed. Please allow a little longer for your journey and follow the 
 signs\, which will direct you via an alternative walking route. Depending 
 on your journey\, this route may be via street level. To pay the correct 
 fare\, just touch out as you exit and touch back in again\, as you 
 re-enter.
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR